@page "/"

<PageTitle>Oceanside Dental Centre - Nanaimo Dentist</PageTitle>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="hero-section position-relative mb-5 d-flex align-items-end" style="background-image: url('images/home-hero.jpg');">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container position-relative">
        <div class="hero-caption p-4 text-white shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Oceanside Dental Centre</h2>
            <p class="mb-1">175 Corfield St S, Parksville, BC V9P 2G1</p>
            <p class="mb-0 fs-4 fw-bold text-white">Call Us: 250.586.4404</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Welcome Section -->
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 text-center">
            <h2 class="welcome-header mb-4">Welcome and thank you for visiting our website!</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted">
                Dr. Blerina Muzina and the Oceanside Dental Centre team are pleased to provide you with high-quality dentistry in a comfortable and caring environment.
            </p>
            <p>
                We are committed to helping you achieve and maintain excellent oral health.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Info Blocks -->
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- General Practice -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                <h5 class="info-header text-white bg-primary-custom p-3 m-0">General Practice</h5>
                <div class="info-body p-3 border border-top-0">
                    <p class="card-text text-justify">The Team at Oceanside Dental welcome you to our Family Centered Practice. We are committed to making all of your appointments a positive and comfortable experience. Our services provide you with individual care, specifically focused on your personal dental wants and needs. We are highly trained and experienced professionals that offer Full-Service Family and Cosmetic Dentistry. Please journey through our website, and learn more about the vast range of services and options that are available to our patients.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- New Patients -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                 <h5 class="info-header text-white bg-sage p-3 m-0">New Patients</h5>
                <div class="info-body p-3 border border-top-0">
                    <p class="card-text text-justify">If you are a New Patient to our office, the first visit will be approximately 2 hours, during this time we will thoroughly assess your present dental condition, have your teeth cleaned and then discuss any treatment needs or requests you may be considering. Included is a three part questionnaire consisting of patient information, health/medical information, dental insurance, employer details and lastly a signed consent to be treated form. Please allow us to serve you better by arriving 10 minutes prior to your scheduled appointment, with your forms completed.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dental Health Importance -->
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                 <h5 class="info-header text-white bg-primary-custom p-3 m-0">Importance of Dental Health</h5>
                <div class="info-body p-3 border border-top-0">
                    <p class="card-text text-justify">Maintaining good oral health is about more than just a beautiful smile; it is essential for your overall well-being. Poor oral hygiene can lead to gum disease and tooth decay, which have been linked to heart disease, diabetes, and other serious health issues. Making dental care a priority in your daily routine ensures not only a radiant smile but also a healthier, happier life for you and your family.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
